Package: calcofi4db
Title: CalCOFI Database Tools
Version: 2.1.0
URL: https://calcofi.io/calcofi4db
BugReports: https://github.com/calcofi/calcofi4db/issues
Authors@R: 
    person("Ben", "Best", , "ben@ecoquants.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2686-0784"))
Description: Tools for ingesting datasets into the CalCOFI database with
    functions to read source CSV files, detect changes in tables and fields,
    and update the database with proper metadata. Includes cloud storage
    (GCS), Parquet, and DuckDB operations for modern data workflows.
